ormula for computing the covariance matrix</a></p></li><li><p><a href=3D"ht=
tps://www.statlect.com/fundamentals-of-probability/covariance-matrix#hid6">=
More details</a></p><ol><li><p><a href=3D"https://www.statlect.com/fundamen=
