0" src=3D"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAANvf7wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAA=
BAAEAAAICRAEAOw=3D=3D" alt=3D"[eq8]" style=3D"background-position:0px -1772=
px;"></span>
</p>
<p>
