40" src=3D"https://www.statlect.com/images/covariance-matrix__32.png" alt=
=3D"[eq10]"></span>
</p>
<h2 id=3D"hid5" class=3D"subsection"><a id=3D"formul"></a>Formula for compu=
ting the
covariance matrix</h2>
<p>
