=3D"116" src=3D"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAANvf7wAAACH5BAEAAAAAL=
AAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw=3D=3D" alt=3D"[eq24]" style=3D"background-position:0p=
x -1px;"></span>
</p>
